Description:
    It will create a migration, initializer and locale files

Example:
    rails generate bizarroids:slider:install

    This will create:
        db/migrate/create_bizarroids_slider_tables.rb
        config/initialiser/bizarroids_slider.rb
        config/locales/bizarroids_slider.en.yml
        config/locales/bizarroids_slider.ru.yml

    This will add:
        routes to config/routes.rb
